column5: We've been doing quite well lately...highlight of last week was feeling monster headshakes, and then seeing GOLD      And one from this morning.    Cheers
Wow! The brown is a tank!   TDunn
nice fall brown for sure !!! chrome is nice too...
incredible fish.......what a treat to see that flash of ontario gold !!   great job

Thanks guys, the brownie gobbled a big purple jig that I tied - I was surprised when I found the jig a mile down it's yap, usually big male browns don't do a whole lot of eating once they're in the rivers
Nice work Kemper!! I have yet to hit the creeks this year...time to get the float rod out it seems!  Amazing brown!
Beautiful fish.  How dare you wear a golf hat on the river.   You rebel.
killer fish! well done man, well done!
Yowsers! With the downturn in the financial world, gold and silver are safe bets! Nice catches!
